      • getSharedValueRef

        AbstractSharedValue getSharedValueRef()
        Returns the AbstractSharedValue implementation this local value references. This method returns null if the reference is invalid.

      • getSharedValue

        int getSharedValue()
        Returns the foreign-key to the shared value. A zero indicates a definite null reference; however, non-zero values may also refer to no value.
